# touch-grass demo — recorded with charmbracelet/vhs
# Run: vhs demo.tape

Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 13
Set Width 920
Set Height 560
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set Padding 24
Set BorderRadius 10
Set LineHeight 1.3

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Sleep 400ms
Type "bash demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 14s
